pageContext.claim: “And when I go to Texas and Florida and drive down the highways and you have 100,000 people on those highways, all the way from either 20, 25 minute drive and you have, I mean, tens and tens of thousands of people waving.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump always inflates his crowd sizes but this is over the top even for him. Do the math on 100,000 people standing on the side of a road.
